{"tid":1294671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 呢個獎一定要提名香港人！！！","createTime":"2019-07-07T22:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:58:07.000Z","uid":269494,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"69a0f935d0bc990c26c268729e373cf19bdfbe45","tid":1294671,"uid":269494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:25:47.000Z","msg":"利申： P牌 但希望你睇左內容再決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mitdisobedienceaward.fluidreview.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmitdisobedienceaward.fluidreview.com%2F&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=ed4ab6fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mitdisobedienceaward.fluidreview.com/</a><br />\n呢個獎叫 &quot;MIT Media Lab Disobedience Award&quot;，我自己譯佢做「麻省理工學院媒體實驗室不服從獎」<br />\n<br />\n呢個獎一定要提名香港人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以提名組織、個人、或者一組人/團體，<br />\n個原則係要非暴力、有創造力、有勇氣、同有承擔個人責任，<br />\n所以可以提名「和理非」、或者「612 人道支援基金」- 歡迎集思廣益！<br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣野 - &quot;Individuals, groups, or organizations cannot nominate themselves.&quot; 即係<br />\n個人，團體或組織不能提名自己...所以呢點令我地身為香港人唔可以提名自己「香港人」，但我地可以提名另一個會令香港人受益既單位/組織<br />\n例如，我以香港人非學生身份，提名香港學生<br />\n<br />\n個重點係贏左可以有美金$250,000，到時可以用黎救義士，再全球出廣告登報等等！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"7583ea7edf61bbd9a8b8de59240d8c9d4eed7889","tid":1294671,"uid":199606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:30:54.000Z","msg":"我唔知可以做啲咩<br />\n所以推啊<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"b1c8b84fd8949e82722c9c8c482dce72615c740c","tid":1294671,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:32:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"239fbd9fb0b05ecbfe9ff7bc3b3e4a1909214e83","tid":1294671,"uid":138233,"like":0,"disli